commit.message:
Update data cache with individual test results incrementally instead of replacing the cache altogether  (#52)

* Added incomplete mesh results data samples for stub_api_server

* Update data cache with individual test results incrementally

* Review1 comments

* Remove rows from MeshResults in favour of ConnectionMatrix

* Added test timestamp range header

* Strict matrix rows and columns ordering

* Removed 'Data stale' warning

* Review2 comments

* Use latest health timeseries item as MatrixView data

* Fix matrix cells coloring and labeling based on packet loss

* Restore stub_api_server linting

* Review3  comments

* Review4 comments

* Bump build-essentials in Dockerfile 12.6 -> 12.9
